<Link id="l00310" /><CodeLine lineNumber="310"><Highlight kind="normal">  &#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00311" /><CodeLine lineNumber="311"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Hard float for mips16 means essentially to compile as soft float</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00312" /><CodeLine lineNumber="312"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// but to use a runtime library for soft float that is written with</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
